    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/cd209f60b9d4d373578747018b02e57c.poster.avif?t=1745567378\" width=630 height=135 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/cd209f60b9d4d373578747018b02e57c.webm?t=1745567378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>退休邮递员韩昭生患病多年记忆逐渐衰退，可梦里的桃花树一直在他脑中挥之不去，他执意认为爱人杨七妹就在树下等待着他。<br><br>韩昭生残存的记忆也因此唤醒。退休后与家人相处的点滴，山里跑邮时与村民们交往的片段，孩子出生的时刻，年轻时从军的经历，一一浮现在他眼前，每个过往的回忆里，韩昭生都在追寻爱人杨七妹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/c55bd88de342d47a8716a8271e6cd9db.poster.avif?t=1745567378\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/c55bd88de342d47a8716a8271e6cd9db.webm?t=1745567378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/c55bd88de342d47a8716a8271e6cd9db.mp4?t=1745567378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>随着病情的加重，韩昭生逐渐模糊了现实与记忆的边界，不分日夜黑白，不知亲朋好友，唯一不变的是，他始终记得在桃花树下等待的七妹。韩昭生的家人不愿他带着遗憾离去，决定寻找他口中的桃花树，以及他和七妹的许诺之地。处于人生最后时刻的韩昭生，能否在梦中的那棵桃花树下看见逝去多年的爱人杨七妹呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/254ad3d96a2dae05aac0c2b2a06f0bda.webp?t=1745567378\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2088030/extras/254ad3d96a2dae05aac0c2b2a06f0bda.poster.avif?t=1745567378\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=333 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto